data.description: Gated Community! Amazing property location! Spacious Ground Floor Condo! This One Bedroom One Bathroom Home Features Great Room concept with Good Flow from Living/Dining Room area into Kitchen with lots of Kitchen Storage and Counterspace. Walk down the hall to a oversized Main Bedroom with two separate bedroom closet areas. Bathroom has dual access from bedroom and hallway and features a large garden tub. Walk outside to your private porch area with additional storage and Washer/Dryer included! Community features a Pool/Spa and Clubhouse. NEW AC in 2023.  Parking is in close proximity to property.
